|                   |    .---->|         0         |<----.    |                   |
+-------------------+    |     |                   |     |    |                   |
|                   |    |     +-------------------|     |    |                   |
|        A          |----'     |                   |     |    |                   |
|                   |          |                   |     |    |                   |
+-------------------+          |                   |     |    |                   |
|                   |          |                   |     |    |                   |
|                   |          |                   |     |    |                   |
|                   |          |                   |     |    +-------------------+
|                   |          |                   |     |    |                   |
|                   |          |                   |     '----|         A'        |
|                   |          |                   |          |                   |
|                   |          |                   |          +-------------------+
|                   |          |                   |          |                   |
+-------------------+          +-------------------+          +-------------------+
EOF

